RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT * FROM ((SELECT a.Contract_Ref_No, b.Disbursement_Mode,NULL Valdt, c.currency, c.amount_financed, c.amount FROM Oltbs_Contract a, Oltbs_Contract_Preference b, Oltbs_Contract_master C WHERE b.Contract_Ref_No = a.Contract_Ref_No AND a.Contract_Status = 'A' AND a.Module_Code = 'OL' AND a.Branch = Global.Current_Branch AND b.Disbursement_Mode = 'M' AND a.Contract_Ref_No = c.Contract_Ref_No and a.LATEST_VERSION_NO = c.version_no AND ((a.auth_status = 'A' /*AND A.CURR_EVENT_CODE <> 'DSBR'*/) OR ((a.auth_status <> 'A' AND (select EVENT_CODE from oltb_contract_event_log ae where ae.contract_ref_no = a.Contract_Ref_No and ae.EVENT_CODE in ('DSBB') and ae.AUTH_STATUS = 'U') in('DSBB')) OR (a.auth_status <> 'A' AND (select EVENT_CODE from oltb_contract_event_log ae where ae.contract_ref_no = a.Contract_Ref_No and ae.EVENT_CODE in ('DSBR','RVDB') and ae.AUTH_STATUS = 'U') in('RVDB', 'DSBR'))))) UNION (SELECT a.Contract_Ref_No, b.Disbursement_Mode, b.Due_Date AS Valdt, c.currency, c.amount_financed, c.amount FROM Oltbs_Contract a, Oltbs_Contract_Dsbr_Sch b, Oltbs_Contract_master C WHERE b.Contract_Ref_No = a.Contract_Ref_No AND a.Contract_Status = 'A' AND a.Module_Code = 'OL' AND a.Branch = Global.Current_Branch AND b.Disbursement_Mode = 'A' AND b.Due_Date <= Global.Application_Date AND Nvl(b.Schedule_Applied, 'N') = 'N' AND Nvl(b.Sch_Reversed, 'N') = 'N' AND a.Contract_Ref_No = c.Contract_Ref_No and a.LATEST_VERSION_NO = c.version_no AND ((a.auth_status = 'A' /*AND A.CURR_EVENT_CODE <> 'DSBR'*/) OR (a.auth_status <> 'A' AND (select EVENT_CODE from oltb_contract_event_log ae where ae.contract_ref_no = a.Contract_Ref_No and ae.EVENT_CODE in ('DSBR','RVDB') and ae.AUTH_STATUS = 'U') in ('RVDB','DSBR')))) UNION (SELECT a.Contract_Ref_No, 'I' AS Disbursement_Mode, a.Value_Date Valdt, c.currency, c.amount_financed, c.amount FROM Oltbs_Contract_Init_Due a, Oltbs_Contract b, Oltbs_Contract_master C WHERE a.Value_Date <= Global.Application_Date AND b.Contract_Status = 'Y' AND b.Branch = Global.Current_Branch AND b.Module_Code = 'OL' AND b.Contract_Ref_No = a.Contract_Ref_No AND b.Contract_Ref_No = c.Contract_Ref_No and b.LATEST_VERSION_NO = c.version_no AND ((b.auth_status = 'A' /*AND A.CURR_EVENT_CODE <> 'DSBR'*/) OR (b.auth_status <> 'A' AND (select EVENT_CODE from oltb_contract_event_log ae where ae.contract_ref_no = b.Contract_Ref_No and ae.EVENT_CODE in ('RVDB','DSBR') and ae.AUTH_STATUS = 'U') in ('RVDB','DSBR'))))) ORDER BY Contract_Ref_No, Disbursement_Mode
